Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an8}字幕搬運：大風鈴   來自極影字幕組、bilibili
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an8}業餘謄抄，僅供交流學習
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,天天都熬夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,給  便當
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,吶  真的不用媽媽去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-運動會  -不用  別來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:00:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在寫小說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.86,0:01:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸也經歷過這種年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,做你想做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這才是青春的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.37,0:01:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我的小說還沒給身邊的人看過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,因為太宰說過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,「人影響不了別人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,同時也無法受人影響」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:02:00.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,なんとなく頭の中で君が  離れなくなっていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:02:00.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,不知為何  你的身影一直縈繞在我的腦海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.54,0:02:21.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,途切れの会話だね いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.54,0:02:21.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我們倆的對話總是斷斷續續呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:29.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,息も吐き出せないほどのことを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:29.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,和你交談時  我總覺得呼吸困難
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:32.35,OPJP,,0,0,0,,目が合った瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:32.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,在眼神交會的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:42.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,また何かが胸を貫いてゆく  今!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:42.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我感覺彷彿有什麼擊中了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:49.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,大好きな人がイマココに居る、居るんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:49.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,現在我最喜歡的人就在我眼前  在我眼前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:56.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,最高の毎日は恋の晴れパレーパレード
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:56.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,每天都幸福得像戀愛大遊行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:03:03.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,近づきたい 誰よりも君に今、いま以上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:03:03.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我想靠近你  我想靠得比誰都近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:13.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,会いたくて会いに行く  笑顔また見つけに行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:13.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我想見你  我現在就去尋找你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,參加女子200公尺的選手  請在入場處集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,今年的贏家是藍組
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,千夏幹勁十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,運動會好歹得表現一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,開始緊張了……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,請女子200公尺選手入場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來是女子200公尺賽跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,吶  不覺得頭巾很醜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,熬夜了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,快到截稿日了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,新人獎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,想的美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,快交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,加油  紅組
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,小太郎參加什麼項目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,男子200公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真慘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,簽運太爛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  馬上輪到小茜賽跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,加油  小茜親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,帥死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊  屁股屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我還有器材組的工作要忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,對了  吶  要是黃組贏了你請客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,飲料就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,勝券在握？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼這麼有信心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒信心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,要我贏了你請飲料？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可以啊  反正贏的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟們  拿出男子漢氣概來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  園田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,別隨便喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,紅組升到了頭名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,贏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我履行職責了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,職責？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,腕力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:06:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,該出場了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真不想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好好丟臉去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,太宰說過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,「被嘲笑再被嘲笑  然後變強」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,只不過我可不想被嘲笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,項目四  男子200公尺賽跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來到誰了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,翹毛君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,安曇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,跑得快嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,欸  完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒  第一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可以啊  二年生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-從第七組開始輪到三年生出場了  -比良
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好啦 要全力衝刺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哇  比良好快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,對手太猛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,被超了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？什麼什麼  剛才那什麼情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有一腿？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,沒  完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不覺得比良很帥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你們在田徑部關係很好吧  小茜親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,乾脆交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不是……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  等我向老師報告完就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,老師現在不在  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在跑道上摔了一跤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說你是翹毛君？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,跟小茜一個班的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是小茜跟我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,班裡有個人翹毛很嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那要我給你處理一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,先在那邊好好沖洗傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我在外面洗過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,洗得很乾淨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哇  好近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不用消毒什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不用  這樣好得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-疼  -抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好粗糙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,餓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺這是最後一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽就努力了一把
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,多吃點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,吃太多小心跑不動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩一場了  分組對抗接力賽跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛  那什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,跟田徑部的大賽比起來就是易如反掌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  那是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸帶攝影機了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可得好好拍下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,別啊  羞死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,接力不是運動會的明珠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,壓軸戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子她爸  別給她壓力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜會緊張的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,下午的比賽還有10分鐘開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,請選手前往各組帳篷集合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,另外  參加借物賽跑的選手們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,請於入場處集合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  水野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,下午也麻煩各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在女生準備借物賽跑期間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,請男生做好下場比賽的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得下一場是……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧？  水野  賽程表有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,借物賽跑結束後……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,障礙賽跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,前面這些移到牆邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,先把跳箱和平衡木搬到門口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那就開始準備工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好  開幹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-這邊  -嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,水野  謝謝你的賽程表
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:12:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,二年生的比賽要結束囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,都放進去沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,吶  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  咧？放哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,只拿出來過一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  空的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,盒子是空的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,三年生的紙條在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  在這裡面拿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  寫的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1212,612)}喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,吶  在這附近有沒有看見我的地瓜吉祥物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,地瓜……是那東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不太妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,地瓜？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,紅組
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一年生  喊出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,下場贏了就是總冠軍了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,黃組也很強的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,還有比良呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來的比賽是  項目16
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:14:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,分組對抗接力賽跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,本日最後一項比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起來加油  讓比賽更熱烈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,地瓜找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,目前領先的是紅組
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來是黃組  藍組  白組
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,差距很小
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,勝負要到最後一刻才揭曉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,黃組第一個衝過終點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來是藍組  白組衝過終點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,最後是紅組  剛衝過終點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,待統計結束後將進行頒獎典禮  閉幕式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,請同學們到本部列隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,搞砸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  男生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,別說了  多可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜親也努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,別放心上  小茜親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼男生就愛說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:17:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她們喊我來的……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很難受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,還好不是正式比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,預選賽可得認真起來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟目標是縣大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,水野一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,太搞笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然掉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你們倆別說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這個  是水野的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,撿到的  在器材放置處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我只要沒這個就會緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我很怕被一堆人看著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真是羞死了  不過我還是喜歡跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我真沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,沒  哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一點都不羞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得水野就這樣挺好的……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(837,531)\frz14.65}今天多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1626,240)\frz340.9}今天多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(918,279)\frz338.8}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz332\pos(596,681)}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1227,846)\frz339}翹毛君
